      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 366,
      "message": "Hi Thierry,\nyou may look at the ElAlto Release, where the MSB http interface still existed.\nBut in Frankfurt (below output in master installation) this interface is removed (see OOM changes 19./20.11.2019).\nSo in my opinion there should be a solution using the https interface in MSB or put a note, that this description is only valid for ElAlto.\nBest regards\nAndreas\n\nubuntu@control01-onap-master:~$ kubectl get service -n onap|grep msb\nmsb-consul                         ClusterIP      10.43.243.108   <none>                                 8500/TCP                                                      7h10m\nmsb-discovery                      ClusterIP      10.43.139.248   <none>                                 10081/TCP                                                     7h10m\nmsb-eag                            NodePort       10.43.232.16    <none>                                 443:30284/TCP                                                 7h10m\nmsb-iag                            NodePort       10.43.254.42    <none>                                 443:30283/TCP                                                 7h10m",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2679,
        "name": "Andreas Geissler",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "andreas@geisibee.de",
        "username": "andreasgeissler"
